videos.description: Royce Freeman takes the handoff to the outside for a 23-yard gain in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Oregon's Freeman finds opening for big gain

videos.description: Royce Freeman puts Oregon on the board with a 2-yard touchdown, tying the Pac-12 Rushing TD record with 59 career total.
videos.headline: Freeman puts Ducks on board with TD

videos.description: Darrell Garretson finds Timmy Hernandez for a short gain on the outside, but the hit from Oregon's Ugochukwu Amadi forces the fumble to give the Ducks the ball.
videos.headline: Ducks force 1st turnover

videos.description: Oregon State's Darell Garretson lets a pass fly over the middle to Timmy Hernandez for a 43-yard touchdown to put the Beavers on the board.
videos.headline: Garretson connects with Hernandez for long TD

videos.description: Justin Herbert throws an over the shoulder pass to Jaylon Redd for a 49-yard gain late in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Oregon's Redd reels in tipped catch

videos.description: Justin Herbert fires a pass over the middle to Jacob Breeland for a 12-yard touchdown to start the second quarter.
videos.headline: Oregon's Herbert slings 2nd TD pass

videos.description: Oregon's Royce Freeman takes the handoff to the outside for a 13-yard touchdown, giving him 60 total touchdowns for his career.
videos.headline: Freeman breaks Pac-12 Rushing TD record

videos.description: Jaylon Redd takes the jet sweep to the outside for a 19-yard touchdown to extend the Ducks lead.
videos.headline: Redd extends Ducks lead on rushing TD

videos.description: Oregon State's Darell Garretson tries forcing a pass into double coverage but is picked off by Thomas Graham Jr.
videos.headline: Ducks force 1st interception

videos.description: Kani Benoit takes the handoff to the outside for a 27-yard rush to put the Ducks in the red zone.
videos.headline: Benoit puts Oregon in red zone on long run

videos.description: Justin Herbert takes the option rush to the outside for a 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Herbert fakes out Beavers for rushing TD

videos.description: Justin Herbert sends a pass deep down the sidelines to Dillon Mitchell for a 53-yard touchdown reception.
videos.headline: Mitchell's 2nd TD extends Ducks lead

videos.description: Jalen Jelks deflects the pass attempt and the ball falls into the hands of Justin Hollins, who returns it for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Oregon gets pick-6 on deflected pass

videos.description: Kani Benoit takes the handoff and finds an opening for a 47-yard touchdown as the Ducks continue to cruise.
videos.headline: Oregon's Benoit breaks out for long TD
